---
import DownloadButton from "./DownloadButton.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="container mx-auto py-16 px-4">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 items-start">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-white">
      About
    </h2>

    <p class="text-xl font-light text-[#8c8c8c] leading-relaxed">
      I build websites and web applications with
      <span class="text-[#F8F8F8]"> React </span>
      and
      <span class="text-[#F8F8F8]"> Astro</span>. For legacy projects I work
      with <span class="text-[#F8F8F8]">WordPress</span>.
    </p>

    <p class="text-xl font-light text-[#8c8c8c] leading-relaxed">
      Currently, I am focusing on back-end development, particularly with
      <span class="text-[#F8F8F8]"> .NET</span> and
      <span class="text-[#F8F8F8]"> Spring Boot</span>.
    </p>

    <p class="text-xl font-light text-[#8c8c8c] leading-relaxed">
      I started out as a <span class="text-[#F8F8F8]">QA tester</span>, that's
      still how I approach every project. I don't consider something done until
      it holds up under <span class="text-[#F8F8F8]">real usage</span>.
    </p>

    <DownloadButton
      href="./curriculum_vitae_alessio_pinto.pdf"
      label="Download resume"
    />
  </div>
</section>
